                <text dataDate="2015-11-16-13-02-10">The artist was working at the court of Shah ‘Abbas the Great (reigned 1588-1629); this work shows his renowned inventive palette and calligraphic line. The lovers are drawn as inextricably bound together, merged volumes confined within one outline.</text>
